  <main id="main">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="wrap">
        <span class="eyebrow">About</span>
        <h1>The recruitment arm of The Spruce Company.</h1>
        <p class="lead">Cleaning Jobs is how suitable cleaners apply once and become eligible for Spruce-standard cleaning work across New Zealand.</p>
        <div class="hero-cta">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/apply/">Apply now <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></a>
          <a class="btn btn-outline" href="/how-it-works/">How it works</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block tint">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="reliable-split">
          <div class="reliable-left">
            <span class="eyebrow">What we are</span>
            <h2>One clear way into Spruce cleaning work.</h2>
            <p class="callout">Apply once. Reviewed once. Considered for suitable work.</p>
            <p>Cleaning Jobs is the recruitment and onboarding arm of The Spruce Company in New Zealand. Instead of applying role by role, suitable cleaners apply through one pathway and are considered for suitable work based on location, demand, availability, certification, and fit.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tick-panel">
            <div class="tick-list">
              <div class="tick-row"><span class="check" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M5 12l4 4 10-10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span class="lbl">One application, kept on file</span></div>
              <div class="tick-row"><span class="check" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M5 12l4 4 10-10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span class="lbl">Onboarding and verification in one process</span></div>
              <div class="tick-row"><span class="check" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M5 12l4 4 10-10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span class="lbl">Training to the Spruce standard</span></div>
              <div class="tick-row"><span class="check" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M5 12l4 4 10-10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span class="lbl">Considered for suitable work allocation</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="why-split">
          <div class="why-left">
            <span class="eyebrow">Connected to Spruce</span>
            <h2>Backed by The Spruce Company.</h2>
            <p>Cleaning Jobs feeds one consistent pipeline of cleaners into Spruce work, so the network can grow by region without lowering standards. Cleaning services are delivered through <a href="https://sprucehome.co.nz/">The Spruce Company</a>.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="why-panel">
            <div class="why-rows">
              <div class="why-row"><span class="n">01</span><div><h3>Residential cleaning</h3><p>Day-to-day and one-off cleans for households across New Zealand.</p></div></div>
              <div class="why-row"><span class="n">02</span><div><h3>Commercial cleaning</h3><p>Recurring and scheduled cleans for offices, retail, and commercial sites.</p></div></div>
              <div class="why-row"><span class="n">03</span><div><h3>Specialist &amp; trades-adjacent</h3><p>Builders&rsquo; cleans, carpet and upholstery support, and add-on services.</p></div></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block tint" id="contact">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="sec-head">
